sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant PD as ProtocolDetector
    participant HS as WebSocketHandshaker
    participant SE as DefaultWebSocketSession

    C->>HS: GET /ws HTTP/1.1<br/>Upgrade: websocket<br/>Connection: Upgrade<br/>Sec-WebSocket-Key: dGhl...<br/>Sec-WebSocket-Version: 13

    Note over PD: 초기 512바이트 스캔
    HS->>PD: detect(ByteBuffer)
    PD->>PD: buffer.mark() 읽기 buffer.reset()
    PD-->>HS: WEBSOCKET 반환

    Note over HS: 1단계 - 필수 헤더 검증
    HS->>HS: Upgrade == websocket?
    HS->>HS: Connection.contains(upgrade)?
    HS->>HS: Sec-WebSocket-Version == 13?

    alt 검증 실패
        HS-->>C: HTTP/1.1 400 Bad Request
    else 검증 성공
        Note over HS: 2단계 - Sec-WebSocket-Accept 계산
        HS->>HS: combined = key + MAGIC_GUID
        HS->>HS: sha1Hash = SHA-1(combined)
        HS->>HS: accept = Base64(sha1Hash)

        HS-->>C: HTTP/1.1 101 Switching Protocols<br/>Upgrade: websocket<br/>Sec-WebSocket-Accept: ...

        Note over C,SE: WebSocket 연결 수립!
        HS->>SE: DefaultWebSocketSession 생성
        SE->>SE: OnOpen 메서드 호출
    end
